channel.title: Elysian - Development team!
channel.description:
[center][CENTER][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ex4qYwM.png[/img][/CENTER] [b]Introduction:[/b]
Hello, I'm looking for atleast 2-3 developers who wants to join the Elysian development team. I have big plans for this project and I will host it in the future so I'm looking for more developers to help me make this project really good. I need someone who is loyal and who is willing to put effort into the project. The server type will be economy & community based.
[b]Application:[/b]
If you would like to join the development team, please drop me a PM or reply to this thread showing your previous work.
[b]Server development thread:[/b]
[URL=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,660242.0.html]Elysian[/URL]
[/center]
